      "date": "2019-01-28 20:38:03.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\n(1 comment)\n\nAurelien,\n\nJust FYI, Maloo is down right now, so don't expect to see any testing until probably tomorrow.",
